posting_body: ['To schedule a tour', 'We now book our tour appointments online!', 'Please call or text us at', 'show contact info', 'to self-schedule from your phone!', 'Book your appointment online today or anytime 24/7!', 'Property Description', 'Located in Livermore, California, Terra at Portola Park offers gorgeous garden-style one, two, and three bedroom apartments.', 'Come join our cozy community with a charming courtyard, glittering swimming pool and resort-inspired hot tub.', 'When you’re not at home, you can visit vineyards, play golf, and explore nearby restaurants and stores.', 'For more outdoorsy days, head to Brushy Peak Regional Preserve just a few minutes away from your friendly community at Terra at Portola Park.', 'Details', 'Availability date:', 'August 3, 2022', 'Pets:', 'Cats, Small Dogs (< 25lb), Large Dogs (> 25lb)', 'Pet notes:', 'Cats and Dogs up to 50lbs allowed with additional pet deposit of $500 and pet rent per month.', "Cat's $65 per month.", 'Dogs $75 per month.', 'Deposit:', '$400-$600 OAC', 'Leasing options:', '12 months', 'Leasing notes:', 'None', 'Application fee:', '$53', 'Amenities', 'Included in Utilities Cost:', 'Utilities Cost:', 'None', 'Laundry:', 'In Unit', 'Parking type:', 'Garage, Covered, Off-Street, On-Street', 'Parking notes:', 'None', 'Appliances:', 'Dishwasher, Refrigerator, Garbage disposal, Microwave, Range/Oven, Washer, Dryer', 'Exterior:', 'Heating/cooling:', 'Heat: forced air, Central AC, Air conditioning, Ceiling fans', 'Wiring:', 'Cable-ready, Wired', 'Facilities and Recreation:', 'Shared pool, Spa', 'Security and Access:', 'Views:', 'Additional features:', 'Quarts countertop', 'Offered by:', 'Terra at Portola Park', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
